column1: Foreign direct investment, net inflows (% of GDP)
SDG 17.3 Mobilize additional financial resources for developing countries from multiple sources
Definition: Sum of equity capital, reinvestment of earnings, other longterm capital and short-term capital, expressed as a percentage of GDP.
Source: World Bank (2020a). World Development Indicators database. Washington, DC. http://data.worldbank.org. Accessed 22 July 2020.
